dct_title_s: Topographischer Atlas der Schweiz (Siefried-Atlas)  = Atlas topographique de la Suisse  (Atlas Siegfried) .
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, contours, spot heights, and landform drawings. Prime meridian is Paris Set does not cover the whole country. Remaining coverage of Switzerland in this series is on 1:50,000 sheets. Title from index map for 1:25,000 scale maps. Also called Atlas Siegfried and Siegfried-Atlas.
